  "2026-04-27T17:20:43.942Z",codex-agent,"Implementation 2026-04-27: replaced static unknown-command examples with runtime-aware remediation generated from active command registries. main.ts now computes command-path suggestions from core + extension command trees and passes guidance context into commander error formatting for text/JSON paths (including bootstrap help JSON unknown-command branch). error-guidance.ts now accepts unknownCommandExamples/unknownCommandNextSteps context and uses it for unknown_command envelopes."
