body: "Implementation checklist:\\n- Build runtime command registry snapshots from active core + extension command paths.\\n- Generate unknown-command remediation examples dynamically from current registry (no static beads/todos examples).\\n- Wire guidance context into commander error formatter for both text and JSON envelopes.\\n- Add/adjust unit and integration coverage for unknown-command guidance examples.\\n- Verify via targeted help/error/runtime tests and record PM evidence."
